pidgin-whatsapp (0.3-1) quantal; urgency=low

  * Fixed some bugs in chat groups
    - Images/files are received in the chat windows
    - Buddy names appear in the chat window
    - Notifications are received OK
  * Fixed escaping of HTML/XML characters such as double quotes
  * Adding offline status
  * Error checking for group chats with proper error notifications
  * Initial status fixed: the status set at startup time is used
  * Fixed memory leaks which caused memory starvation
  * Many other small bug fixes and code refactor

 -- David Guillen Fandos <david@davidgf.net>  Tue, 8 Oct 2013 23:20:00 +0200

